# Repository Language

All text in this repository must be in **English**:

- Documentation (README, DEVELOPMENT_LOG, CHANGELOG, etc.)
- Code comments
- Commit messages
- Variable/function names (English)
- UI strings intended for developers (e.g., dev tooltips, debug logs)

Exception: User-facing UI in the app may use other languages if required by the product.
